queries.sql: SELECT `tb1`.`id`, `tb1`.`semester_id`, `tb1`.`title`, `tb1`.`score`, `tb1`.`day_start`, `tb1`.`day_end`, `tb1`.`image`, `tb1`.`created_at`, `tb1`.`publish`, `tb1`.`canonical`, `tb2`.`title` as `cat_title`, (SELECT fullname FROM users WHERE users.id = tb1.userid_created) as creator FROM `events` as `tb1` INNER JOIN `semesters` as `tb2` ON `tb1`.`semester_id` = `tb2`.`id` WHERE `tb1`.`deleted_at` = 0 GROUP BY `tb1`.`id` ORDER BY `tb1`.`id` desc LIMIT 20

SELECT `tb1`.`id`, `tb1`.`email`, `tb1`.`phone`, `tb1`.`image`, `tb1`.`fullname`, `tb1`.`user_catalogue_id`, ( SELECT tb2.title FROM user_catalogues as tb2 WHERE tb1.user_catalogue_id = tb2.id) as `job` FROM `users` as `tb1` WHERE `email` = 'admin@gmail.com'
